commit.message: Added login endpoint to the Readme

Merge pull request #2 from vatri/swagger-api-docs-

Swagger API docs
Linked Swagger API in Readme. Updates to the Readme.
Remove cart when order is placed. Code cleanup.
Checking token using Redis cache. Code cleanup.
Added order ID to JSON response
Added missing controller for login action
Renamed application.properties to application.properties-sample. Small update to readme.
Started to update Readme. Finished creating order from shopping cart.
Fixed removing items from Redis cached list

Merge pull request #1 from vatri/refactoring-to-cache-redis-

Refactoring the redis to the app's cache interface
Moved CartController to controllers dir. Small bugfix.
Finished Redis cache implementation. Covered with unit tests.
Added few interfaces and 1 test for RedisCache implementation
Added HAL to orders and groups controllers. And some refactoring of resource classes.
Moved SQL file to proper folder
Loaded HATEOAS dependency and few more steps
Order validation and message codes updated
Allowed public access for GET request to Product and Group resources
Finished base for cart endpoints. Todo: create order method in the cart service
Started implementation of Cart module using Redis database
Product image section. Authorization role (authority) checking.
Added product description. Send 403 status on failed authentication. Added SQL dump file.
Send SC_UNATHORIZED response for not authenticated requests.
Product group create, update and read
Bugfix - removed injecting of cookie name
Checking JWT token - prototype. Thanks to https://github.com/bfwg/springboot-jwt-starter
Fixed StackOverflowError of nested entities with using JSON Jackson annontations
Basic product CRUD (without D actually) operations
Init files. Basic product REST controller.
